Directory containing several auxilliary scripts for running INSIGHT-EM
----------------------------------------------------------------------

List of files:
--------------
   1. scripts/runINSIGHT-EM.sh
   2. scripts/getSelectionEstimates.sh
   3. scripts/getBetaEstimates.sh
   4. scripts/labelLHsites.sh
   5. scripts/processEMresults.sh
   6. scripts/addPseudocounts.sh
   7. scripts/getEMstatus.sh

Description: (more details in the header of each script file)
------------
   1. scripts/runINSIGHT-EM.sh  <dataID>  <emInputElements>  <emInputFlanks>  <outDir>  <freqThreshold>  [--pseudo]
      main script for running INSIGHT-EM on data, given a pre-threshold EM input file for the element sites
      and a similar file for the polymorphic neutral flanking sites (or a file containing pre-computed beta estimates).
      produces a log file for all INSIGHT-EM runs, a results summary line, and a posterior probability file
      * calls:  addPseudocounts.sh  getBetaEstimates.sh  getSelectionEstimates.sh  processEMresults.sh
      
   2. scripts/getSelectionEstimates.sh  <elementSummaryFile>  <freqThreshold>  <beta1> <beta2> <beta3>  <logFile>
      runs INSIGHT-EM on a pre-threshold EM input file for the element sites.
      produces estimates of selection parameters (rho, eta, gamma, and derivatives),
      as well as LRT statistics for rho>o, eta>0 and gamma>0.
      expects a frequency threshold f (for L/H distinction of polymorphic sites),
      the neutral beta parameters associated with the partitioning of the site frequency spectrum
      to DAFs of (0,f) ; [f,1-f] ; (1-f,1).
      outputs INSIGHT-EM progress and results to log file. 
      * calls:  labelLHsites.sh  getEMstatus.sh
      
   3. scripts/getBetaEstimates.sh  <flankPolySummaryFile>  <freqThreshold>  <logFile>
      runs INSIGHT-EM on a pre-threshold EM input file for the flanking polymorphic sites.
      produces estimates of beta parameters (beta1, beta2, and beta3).
      expects a frequency threshold f (for L/H distinction of polymorphic sites).
      outputs INSIGHT-EM progress and results to log file. Last line in file contains the beta estimates.
      * calls:  labelLHsites.sh  getEMstatus.sh

   4. scripts/labelLHsites.sh  <summaryFile>  <outFile>  <freqThresold>
      produces a thresholded EM input file from a non-thresholded file
      using a frequency cutoff (freqThresold) for L/H polymorphic sites.
      
   5. scripts/processEMresults.sh  <logFile>  <dataID>  <resultsFile>
      parses an INSIGHT-EM log file (generated by getSelectionEstimates.sh)
      and produces a single results summary line
      
   6. scripts/addPseudocounts.sh  <emInputFile>  [<flankInputFile>]
      adds pseudo counts to EM input file(s)
      
   7. scripts/getEMstatus.sh
      parses an INSIGHT-EM log file and reports status of EM

